1102
01:17:05,325 --> 01:17:07,614
So what does your analyst say?

1103
01:17:07,744 --> 01:17:10,994
Donny's in a coma.
He had a very bad acid experience.

1104
01:17:11,122 --> 01:17:14,657
Oh, that's gr... That's great.
I mean, you know...

1105
01:17:14,792 --> 01:17:18,078
- I think you're making a big mistake here.
- Why?

1106
01:17:18,212 --> 01:17:21,581
