Isaac, I'm sorry.
I really am. I'm really sorry.

1118
01:18:00,252 --> 01:18:02,494
Oh, well, I'm...

1119
01:18:02,630 --> 01:18:05,381
I'm sorr... Where are you going?

1120
01:18:05,507 --> 01:18:07,547
- I gotta get some air.
- Oh.

1121
01:18:46,004 --> 01:18:47,629
What are you doing here?

1122
01:18:47,756 --> 01:18:49,998
I spoke to Mary. Were you gonna tell me?

1123
01:18:50,133 --> 01:18:54,261
- I was, but... I'm trying to teach a class.
- So where can we go and talk?

1124
01:18:54,387 --> 01:18:57,471
- How'd you get past the security?
- I walked right past.

1125
01:18:57,599 --> 01:19:00,802
What are you telling me?
That you're gonna leave Emily

1126
01:19:00,935 --> 01:19:03,640
and run away with
the... the winner of the

