1156
01:20:45,284 --> 01:20:48,618
You just can't live the way you do.
It's all so perfect.

1157
01:20:48,746 --> 01:20:52,197
Jesus, what are future generations
gonna say about us? My God!

1158
01:20:52,333 --> 01:20:55,002
You know, someday
we're gonna be like him.

1159
01:20:55,127 --> 01:20:59,753
