01:24:46,723 --> 01:24:52,309
Ooh, I would say Groucho Marx,
to name one thing.

1208
01:24:54,146 --> 01:24:56,222
And Willie Mays.

1209
01:24:56,357 --> 01:25:01,943
And... the second movement
of the Jupiter Symphony.

1210
01:25:02,655 --> 01:25:08,443
<i>And... Louis Armstrong's
