1228
01:29:48,844 --> 01:29:53,340
What d'you... What d'you mean? If I got
over here two minutes later, you'd be...

1229
01:29:53,473 --> 01:29:55,513
...you'd be going to London?

1230
01:30:00,813 --> 01:30:03,814
Well, let me get right to the point then.

1231
01:30:03,941 --> 01:30:05,768
I don't think you oughta go.

