01:30:05,902 --> 01:30:09,769
I think I made a big mistake.
and I would prefer it if you didn't go.

1233
01:30:09,905 --> 01:30:11,945
Oh, Isaac.

1234
01:30:12,074 --> 01:30:16,487
I mean it. I know it looks real bad now,
but, uh, you know, it...

1235
01:30:16,620 --> 01:30:19,538
Are you seeing anybody?
Are you going with anybody?

1236
01:30:19,665 --> 01:30:21,075
