01:32:38,881 --> 01:32:42,166
Yeah, of course I do, but, you know...

1275
01:32:42,301 --> 01:32:46,630
I mean, I just don't want that thing
about you that I like to change.

1276
01:32:51,059 --> 01:32:53,217
I've gotta make a plane.

1277
01:32:53,353 --> 01:32:56,307
Come on, you don't... Come on.

1278
01:32:56,439 --> 01:32:58,811
You don't... You don't have to go.

1279
01:32:59,859 --> 01:33:03,144
Why couldn't you have
brought this up last week?

1280
01:33:05,865 --> 01:33:08,237
Six months isn't so long.

1281
01:33:10,035 --> 01:33:12,491
Not everybody gets corrupted.

1282
01:33:14,623 --> 01:33:18,074
You have to have a little faith in people.

